    <part Name="MessageWhenFirstSeen" Mode="Popup" Message="{{K|You cannot remember when it was that the dreams first began. Were you a hooded traveler of the windswept plain, taking dream-step after dream-stap towards something half-buried in the salt, transfixed by the glint in the distance? Were you a glowcrow soaring the dreaming sky, sweeping the world below with your gaze, landing time and time again near the crater? Or were you an ant that had strayed from the scent-path, losing yourself past the towers of scumgrass, finding yourself on the earth-lip and finding yourself in the presence of something much taller and blacker than all of the grass-blades you'd seen?}} 

    {{K|It all bleeds together, these days. It bleeds and it pools in the crater before you, for the crater you dreamt of is here.}}" />
